flowchart TB
    subgraph Phase1 [Test Planning]
        P1[Define test objectives]
        P2[Identify modules to test]
        P1 --> P2
    end

    subgraph Phase2 [Test Environment]
        E1[Browser: Chrome or Edge]
        E2[Next.js dev or production build]
        E3[PostgreSQL + Clerk + Gemini API]
        E1 --> E2 --> E3
    end

    P2 --> Phase2

    subgraph Phase3 [Functional Testing]
        T1[Auth and route protection]
        T2[Onboarding and profile]
        T3[Industry dashboard]
        T4[Resume builder]
        T5[Cover letter generator]
        T6[Mock interview quiz]
        T7[Background job - Inngest]
    end

    Phase2 --> T1
    T1 --> T2 --> T3
    T3 --> T4 --> T5 --> T6 --> T7

    subgraph Phase4 [Validation Checks]
        V1[Form validation - Zod]
        V2[Data persistence in DB]
        V3[AI response and save]
        V4[PDF export]
        V5[Security - no API key in browser]
    end

    T7 --> V1 --> V2 --> V3 --> V4 --> V5

    subgraph Phase5 [Result]
        R1{All tests passed?}
        R2[Document results in report]
        R3[Fix defects and retest]
    end

    V5 --> R1
    R1 -->|Yes| R2
    R1 -->|No| R3
    R3 --> Phase3
    R2 --> End([Testing Complete])
